{"tid":1901310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"漁護署指確診新型冠狀病毒患者寵物對病毒呈弱陽性反應","createTime":"2020-02-27T17:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T17:58:48.000Z","uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"612d5b74bfd69f193c339660669ef68ab92923f8","tid":1901310,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1269671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1269671&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0aC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f97ec795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1269671</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漁護署發言人表示，一名確診新型冠狀病毒患者所飼養的狗隻，對病毒測試呈弱陽性反應，狗隻並無任何相關病徵。漁護署現時未有數據證明寵物會感染病毒，但署方對有關狗隻進行密切監察，並進一步抽取樣本化驗，以確定狗隻是已感染病毒，抑或是牠的口鼻從環境中沾染病毒。署方會繼續為有關狗隻進行反覆測試，待結果呈陰性後，才會交還狗隻。署方強烈建議患者將飼養的寵物送往漁護署，接受14天的檢疫和獸醫學監察，及按情況進行病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n署方星期三接獲衞生署轉介，指一名患者的狗隻需交給漁護署。人員同日傍晚到大坑一住所接走狗隻，隨即送往港珠澳大橋口岸動物居留所，並從狗隻的口腔，鼻腔及肛門抽取樣本進行病毒測試，驗出呈弱陽性反應。"},{"pid":"24da5dafa5900562a41d3d6cef10768df9816799","tid":1901310,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/28/P2020022800012.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F28%2FP2020022800012.htm&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0aC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=8a10ed03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/28/P2020022800012.htm</a>"},{"pid":"81ae177350a90f30205d7c01ab371ff7e1db4d17","tid":1901310,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:51:55.000Z","msg":"嚟緊九月就立法會選舉啦<br />\n五月頭就會截止登記<br />\n無論你係地區直選定係功能組別<br />\n各位手足都快啲登記做選民啦<br />\n特別係啱啱足夠18歲嘅各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係最低成本為香港出一分力嘅方法啊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Feform%2FREO-1%28C&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0aC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=7c06d72b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C</a>)_eSign.pdf<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲填左上面呢份表格之後寄返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8450a01b803c0a8f0fbe8bbfe6a23dd61d3cce","tid":1901310,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"原來大陸人做啱左"},{"pid":"05186df6cd7721a5f08314611de91209a7502f66","tid":1901310,"uid":45708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b8450a01b803c0a8f0fbe8bbfe6a23dd61d3cce","tid":1901310,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"原來大陸人做啱左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"大陸人係咪一早就知，但佢地又隱瞞"},{"pid":"7ddef08b33c4b7368ba0186538967d06054a352d","tid":1901310,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"傳染途徑又大左，你話唔係人造我真係唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad5075aaa6a90723b85c19df841be8918f7c6da","tid":1901310,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:58:48.000Z","msg":"人傳動物，但動物無事，再由動物傳俾人？<br />\n<br />\n其實而家啲武肺測試方法感覺好唔可靠"}]}